snippet.title: Probably Archery Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Launch trailer for the full version of Probably Archery.

Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/263420/
Humble Store: https://www.humblebundle.com/store/p/probablyarchery_storefront

Available for PC, Mac and Linux. Single player challenges, team deathmatch, co-op horde mode and Zoccer - Zombie Soccer.

Trailer music: 'Call to Adventure!' and 'Bent and Broken' by Kevin MacLeod (incompetech.com). Licensed under Creative Commons: By Attribution 3.0 http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/3.0/
